          0.8852208601275795,
          0.6959535297403869
        ],
        "order": 13
      },
      {
        "id": "docling_jiaocaineedrop_chap02.pdf_16_22",
        "observed_type": "list_item",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "Analyzing Why did England regard the Dutch and Spanish presence in North America as a threat, and how did England respond?",
        "bbox": [
          0.3438661745061704,
          0.7223837205753602,
          0.6096654306518219,
          0.7834821430711195
        ],
        "order": 18
      },
      {
        "id": "docling_jiaocaineedrop_chap02.pdf_16_25",
        "observed_type": "list_item",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "Analyzing Charts Study the chart on page 54 on Spanish, English, and French colonization. In political organization, what was a trait of the English colonies that the French and Spanish colonies did not share?",
        "bbox": [
          0.6245353116110753,
